# Java Backend Conventions

## Package Structure

```
org.dreamhorizon.pulseserver/
├── resources/          # REST controllers, grouped by domain
│   ├── <domain>/
│   │   ├── <Domain>Controller.java
│   │   ├── Rest<Domain>Mapper.java      # MapStruct (REST ↔ service)
│   │   ├── models/                      # REST request/response DTOs
│   │   └── validators/                  # Validation logic (where needed)
│   └── v1/                              # Versioned endpoints
├── service/            # Business logic, grouped by domain
│   ├── <domain>/
│   │   ├── <Domain>Service.java         # Interface
│   │   ├── impl/
│   │   │   └── <Domain>ServiceImpl.java # Implementation
│   │   └── models/                      # Service-layer models
├── tenant/             # Multi-tenancy domain
│   ├── TenantService.java
│   ├── TenantDao.java
│   ├── TenantFilter.java
│   ├── TenantContext.java
│   └── TenantsController.java
├── dao/                # Data access, grouped by domain
│   ├── <domain>/
│   │   ├── <Domain>Dao.java
│   │   ├── Queries.java                 # SQL as static constants
│   │   ├── Dao<Domain>Mapper.java       # MapStruct (DAO ↔ service)
│   │   └── models/                      # Row/DB models
│   ├── clickhousecredentialsdao/        # ClickHouse tenant credentials
│   ├── tenantdao/                       # Tenant data access
├── client/             # External clients (ClickHouse, MySQL, Athena, S3)
├── config/             # Application configuration
├── constant/           # Shared constants
├── dto/                # Shared DTOs
├── error/              # ServiceError enum
├── errorgrouping/      # Symbolication and error grouping
├── guice/              # Guice injector setup
├── healthcheck/        # Health check endpoints
├── model/              # Shared domain models
├── module/             # Guice modules (*Module.java)
├── rest/               # Response wrappers, error handling
├── util/               # Utilities
├── verticle/           # Vert.x verticles (MainVerticle, RestVerticle)
└── vertx/              # Vert.x helpers
```

**Caveats on structure:**
- `service/<domain>/impl/` is used for complex domains (interaction, configs). Simpler services may keep `*ServiceImpl` at the domain level (e.g., `service/query/QueryServiceImpl.java`).
- `validators/` exists only where complex validation is needed (currently `resources/interaction/validators/`).
- Query classes are usually `Queries.java`, but some domains use `*Query.java` or `*Queries.java` (e.g., `AlertsQuery.java`, `AthenaJobQueries.java`).

## File Naming

| Type | Convention | Examples |
|------|------------|---------|
| REST controllers | `*Controller` | `InteractionController`, `AlertController` |
| Service interfaces | `*Service` | `InteractionService`, `ConfigService` |
| Service implementations | `*ServiceImpl` | `InteractionServiceImpl`, `ConfigServiceImpl` |
| DAOs | `*Dao` | `InteractionDao`, `AlertsDao`, `SdkConfigsDao` |
| SQL constants | `Queries` (preferred) | `dao/interaction/Queries.java` |
| MapStruct mappers | `*Mapper` + `INSTANCE` | `RestInteractionMapper`, `DaoInteractionMapper` |
| Guice modules | `*Module` | `InteractionModule`, `ConfigModule`, `MainModule` |
| Verticles | `*Verticle` | `MainVerticle`, `RestVerticle` |

## Verticle Pattern

- **`MainVerticle`**: loads config (MySQL, ClickHouse, Athena, WebClient), stores in `SharedDataUtils`, deploys `RestVerticle` (one instance per CPU core)
- **`RestVerticle`**: extends `AbstractRestVerticle`, scans package for JAX-RS resources, sets up `GuiceInjector`, configures CORS/router

## Service Layer

- Define an **interface** and an **impl** for complex domains in `service/<domain>/impl/`
- Return RxJava3 `Single<T>`, `Maybe<T>`, or `Completable` — never block
- Inject via Guice: `@RequiredArgsConstructor(onConstructor = @__({@Inject}))`
- Annotate with `@Slf4j` for logging

## DAO Layer

- SQL strings live in a `Queries` class (static `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE` constants)
- Use `MysqlClient` (writer/reader pools) or `ClickhouseQueryService`
- Name classes `*Dao`
- DAO-level row models go in `dao/<domain>/models/`

## DTOs

- Lombok `@Data` on all DTOs
- Jackson `@JsonIgnoreProperties(ignoreUnknown = true)` on response DTOs
- MapStruct mappers with `INSTANCE = Mappers.getMapper(...)` pattern

## Error Handling

- Use `ServiceError` enum (codes like `BE1001`) implementing `RestError`
- Throw via `ServiceError.X.getException()` or `getCustomException(message, cause)`
- Response shape: `Response<T>` with `data` and `Error.of(code, message)`

## REST Controllers

- JAX-RS annotations (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, etc.) from `vertx-rest`
- Use `RestResponse.jaxrsRestHandler()` to bridge RxJava to Vert.x
- Group by domain in `resources/` package

## Validation

- `ConstraintViolation` → 400 with `errors` array
- Validation logic in dedicated `ValidationModule`

## Testing

- JUnit 5 + Mockito + AssertJ
- Test classes mirror main package structure in `src/test/java/`
- Method naming: `should*` (e.g., `shouldThrowExceptionIfInteractionAlreadyPresent`)
- Group tests with `@Nested` classes for logical groups
- JaCoCo enforced: **35% overall**, **80% on changed files**

## Code Style

- Google Checkstyle (`.checkstyle/checks.xml`): 140-char lines, 2-space indent
- No wildcard imports (enforced by Checkstyle `AvoidStarImport`)
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Lombok annotations: `@Data`, `@Slf4j`, `@RequiredArgsConstructor(onConstructor = @__({@Inject}))`
